column5: Came across this site while looking up something else:  http://www.vendio.com/stores/rapalamarket/
Wow !! I haven't seen some of those rapalas since i was a kid.Great site.Thanks
Interesting website - I tried a search for Rapala Count Down Jointed which I have a couple of nothing came up so I don't known if they are a collectible or just out of stock.......

I have a couple of the rare ones in my garage attic above my boat.....some are discontinued because they didn't catch fish or Rapala found a way to alter them slightly reducing production costs to maximize profits.
There vintage section isn't very old. I've got some of the old floating balsa minnows, still in the pale blue boxes they used to pack them in.
u may want to try "ebay" my friend  good luck
